thread.title: Tam Hinchy

author: Tam Hinchy
title: Tam Hinchy
text: I booked online and found the whole process easy from the online booking to the collection service from the airport to the service at the counter. All staff where friendly and helpful, the car was exactly as ordered. The only thing that was not liked is that they hold a payment on your credit card for a week. I think this should be removed when you return the vehicle.
